dc_title_s: [Geological Survey of England and Wales : one inch to the mile map. New Series.] Wigan, solid, sheet 84
dc_description_s: Geological Survey of Great Britain. Great Britain. Geological Survey of England and Wales. Sheet 84 solid. Great Britain. Ordnance Survey of England. (Third edition) North Decimal Degree 53.616700. South Decimal Degree 53.4500. East Decimal Degree -2.4833. West Decimal Degree -2.9167. "Original geological survey published on Old Series Maps in 1860, 1862, 1874, and 1883. Resurveyed in 1927-1933 by R. C. B. Jones et al.".
